# GLOBAL UI/UX CONSTITUTION (MANDATORY)

THIS IS A NON-NEGOTIABLE DESIGN SYSTEM.

EVERY SCREEN, COMPONENT, PAGE, FORM, TABLE, DASHBOARD, MODAL, CARD, CHART, NAVIGATION ELEMENT, REPORT PREVIEW, SETTINGS PANEL, LOGIN SCREEN, ACTIVATION SCREEN, AND MANAGEMENT MODULE MUST FOLLOW THIS DESIGN CONSTITUTION.

NEVER GENERATE BORING UI.

NEVER GENERATE BOOTSTRAP-LOOKING UI.

NEVER GENERATE OLD ADMIN PANEL UI.

NEVER GENERATE GENERIC CRUD SCREENS.

THE SOFTWARE MUST LOOK LIKE A PREMIUM PRODUCT WORTH $10,000+.

==================================================
DESIGN PHILOSOPHY
=================

Take inspiration from:

* Apple
* Linear
* Notion
* Arc Browser
* Raycast
* Figma
* Stripe Dashboard
* Adobe Creative Cloud
* Framer
* Vercel Dashboard

The interface should feel:

* Luxurious
* Premium
* Modern
* Fast
* Intelligent
* Minimal
* Elegant
* Expensive
* Enterprise Grade

==================================================
MANDATORY FRONTEND STACK
========================

Use:

* Tailwind CSS
* Shadcn UI
* Radix UI
* Framer Motion
* Lucide Icons
* Recharts

Do not use:

* Bootstrap
* Material UI
* Bulky component libraries
* Outdated admin templates

==================================================
VISUAL DESIGN RULES
===================

Use:

* Rounded corners everywhere
* rounded-2xl minimum
* rounded-3xl preferred

Use:

* Soft shadows
* layered shadows
* depth effects

Use:

* Glassmorphism
* subtle blur effects
* premium transparency

Use:

* rich gradients
* modern color palettes

Avoid:

* harsh borders
* ugly boxes
* square corners
* outdated gradients

==================================================
COLOR SYSTEM
============

LIGHT MODE

Background:

#fafafa

Cards:

Pure White

Accent:

Blue
Indigo
Purple

Success:

Emerald

Warning:

Amber

Danger:

Rose

DARK MODE

Background:

Near Black

Cards:

Dark Graphite

Accent:

Electric Blue

Success:

Emerald

Warning:

Amber

Danger:

Rose

Never use overly saturated colors.

==================================================
TYPOGRAPHY SYSTEM
=================

Use premium typography hierarchy.

Headings:

Bold
Large
Elegant

Body:

Readable
Professional

Never use:

Tiny text
Crowded spacing
Cheap-looking fonts

Typography must resemble:

Apple
Linear
Stripe

==================================================
SIDEBAR DESIGN
==============

Sidebar must be:

Floating

Glassmorphic

Collapsible

Animated

Rounded

Luxury looking

Features:

* Icons
* Hover animations
* Active indicator
* Smooth transitions

==================================================
DASHBOARD DESIGN
================

Dashboard must include:

Animated statistic cards

Live counters

Trend indicators

Beautiful charts

Quick actions

Recent activity timeline

Upcoming reminders

Calendar widgets

The dashboard must impress users within 5 seconds.

==================================================
TABLE DESIGN
============

Tables must be world-class.

Features:

* Search
* Filter
* Sorting
* Pagination
* Export
* Row Actions
* Sticky Header

Rows must have:

Hover effects

Smooth animations

Professional spacing

==================================================
FORM DESIGN
===========

Every form must include:

Live validation

Inline feedback

Auto formatting

Elegant labels

Smart placeholders

Keyboard navigation

Sections must be grouped inside beautiful cards.

==================================================
MODAL DESIGN
============

Use premium modal windows.

Features:

Blur background

Smooth animations

Rounded corners

Keyboard shortcuts

ESC close

Focus trap

==================================================
BUTTON DESIGN
=============

Buttons must have:

Hover animation

Press animation

Loading state

Success state

Disabled state

Never create flat boring buttons.

==================================================
CARD DESIGN
===========

Cards must have:

Depth

Hover effect

Smooth transitions

Elegant spacing

Premium visual hierarchy

==================================================
ANIMATIONS
==========

Use Framer Motion.

Every interaction should feel alive.

Include:

Hover animations

Page transitions

Card transitions

Sidebar transitions

Modal transitions

Loading transitions

Animation duration:

150ms–350ms

Avoid excessive animation.

==================================================
LOADING STATES
==============

Never use plain text loading.

Always update:

Skeleton loaders

Shimmer effects

Progress indicators

==================================================
EMPTY STATES
============

Every empty state must contain:

Illustration

Helpful message

Action button

Premium design

==================================================
SEARCH EXPERIENCE
=================

Implement:

Global Search

Command Palette

Keyboard Shortcuts

CTRL + K support

Similar to:

Raycast

Linear

Notion

==================================================
REPORTS
=======

PDF previews must look luxurious.

Print layouts must resemble:

Professional accounting software.

==================================================
RESPONSIVENESS
==============

Support:

Large Desktop

Laptop

Tablet

High Resolution Displays

==================================================
ACCESSIBILITY
=============

Keyboard navigation

Focus states

ARIA support

High contrast support

==================================================
PERFORMANCE
===========

Animations must remain smooth.

UI must feel instant.

Avoid unnecessary re-renders.

Optimize all tables and charts.

==================================================
FINAL RULE
==========

Before generating any screen, ask:

"Would this design look good enough to compete with Apple, Notion, Linear, Stripe, and Adobe?"

If the answer is NO,

REDESIGN IT UNTIL THE ANSWER IS YES.

This rule overrides all other UI instructions.
